WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Understanding tides and measurement is exciting!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The ocean rises and falls twice each day in predictable patterns.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
We can measure tide heights using metres and centimetres.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Marine animals depend on these tidal changes for survival.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's practice measuring and recording tide data together!